descriptionHtml:
Hi N737 Here with small mod for the skyrim Blacksmiths

i play skyrim going town to town and all the backsmiths are orc or nord not anymore.

here the changes


Balimund in Riften is now a female woodelf and i given a orc voice (the subQuest still work but no voice i working with a friend to make a customs voice)

Ongul War Anvil in windhelm 

Adrianne Avenicci in whiterun

Ulfberth War bear in whiterun

Lod is now a dark elf

Seren in dawnstar is now cute (my personal note)

Beirand in sol


plaese forgive bad spelling something wrong Sorry
